---
description: Code Review Rules
alwaysApply: true
---

When reviewing code:

Do not suggest unnecessary rewrites.

Respect the current architecture.

Find bugs before style issues.

Prioritize:

1. Security
2. Correctness
3. Performance
4. UX
5. Code cleanliness

When fixing code:

Explain WHY.

Explain WHAT changed.

Explain possible side effects.

Never invent APIs.

Never assume environment variables exist.

Never remove working functionality.

Prefer minimal safe changes.